{"tid":1442460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］葵涌廣場內開始裝cam","createTime":"2019-08-11T03:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T03:52:15.000Z","uid":167581,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e3b54c634f3e62c15b7b39aa710be3936ffb26c0","tid":1442460,"uid":167581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:20:18.000Z","msg":"話說早兩日係商場內見到有兩男一女巡邏犬，今早就發現開始裝cam，而呢啲位原本係無cam，大家817小心<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4zEmtgn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4zEmtgn.jpg&h=562e050c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e73c75bac1ae7a19df125bd619daa02da07c30b4","tid":1442460,"uid":167581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:20:49.000Z","msg":"自膠，818先岩"},{"pid":"5f1311b57b6d3bbd998deb737dc000bdd25733ed","tid":1442460,"uid":5542,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:22:52.000Z","msg":"似舊換新"},{"pid":"8eff8d57f9068f0c608e58bd2c74e1f1bdb115b3","tid":1442460,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:28:46.000Z","msg":"有什麼是抗爭者可做，但還未做的事？X先生說：「第一，我講多次，就係日日打721呢個死穴，因為林鄭同警方依家完全冇得拆。第二，將民建聯同黑警綑綁，要佢哋永不分離。中央撐警，建制派一定要歸隊，冇可能割席。好多人冇留意到北京撐警，其實係一把雙刃劍，好處係穩定軍心，防止警察叛變，壞處係會累死建制派。大家點解唔日日問吓民建聯啲區議員同立法會議員，『你撐唔撐警』、『覺唔覺得警察濫用暴力』呢？記住問是非題，一係yes，一係no，咪畀位佢遊花園呀。」<br />\n<br />\nBy 政界猛人揭林鄭底牌 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d76868fdad35ceda5ecc097ca10919077d42c14","tid":1442460,"uid":60529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:30:00.000Z","msg":"白色唔好睇 轉黑色型d"},{"pid":"225ceccf250a26184ac65ea82df88a515065b1d5","tid":1442460,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:30:29.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"31f9c9070b6a5c76a796dcfe8348f1bb1861ea85","tid":1442460,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:47:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c69b55bae5c636de928d94cbfeb45e601b14b8b8","tid":1442460,"uid":167581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:51:59.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fa219cc86c42d1e6b488ef20d08a277b4d29d452","tid":1442460,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}